%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-nh%C3%A2n/poem-N0_vkZSmmsNk1Fl9jhCmmQ">Ký Tán thượng nhân - 寄贊上人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Thanh-minh/poem-3YDWV6YBQVyQBygAwpaO-g">Thanh minh - 清明</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%8Bch-phong/poem-oeXd7-PMf-mvXh8JPO9RUQ">Tịch phong - 夕烽</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/T%C4%A9nh-Y%C3%AAn-v%C3%A3n-l%E1%BA%ADp/poem-IYFJBs-9dLj8I--pA1m2jw">Tĩnh Yên vãn lập - 靖安晚立</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%C3%AAu-C%E1%BA%A5u/Xu%C3%A2n-thi/poem-7E6wITnxCld9Svvhs4uUkw">Xuân thi - 春詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%C3%AAu-C%E1%BA%A5u/author-Ae4EcQjuDrs0y-frjFfqIA">Tiêu Cấu</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
